      - text: 林克！
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 10
      - text: "你拯救了卓拉领地，\n我衷心地感谢你卓哟！\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 1
      - text: 领地里的大伙们也都很高兴！
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 20
      - text: "\n没有比这更值得令人开心的了！"
  talk01:
    attributes: Npc_Zora003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 5
            - 6
      - text: 但是，林克……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 20
      - text: "\n我有件事想要问你卓哟。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - text: "你活着从水之神兽\n"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 瓦·露塔
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "的体内出来了。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 1
      - text: "但是，米法却没有回来……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 16
      - text: 也就是说……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 20
      - text: "\n已经为时已晚了吗？"
      - control:
          kind: single_choice
          label: 0
  talk02:
    attributes: Npc_Zora003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 4
            - 6
      - text: "灵，灵魂……\n\n那么也就是说，米法她已经……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 20
      - text: "\n她有说什么吗卓哟？"
  talk04:
    attributes: Npc_Zora003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 12
      - text: 是吗……米法……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 20
      - text: "\n怎么会这样……她是我的骨肉，\n我却什么都做不了卓哟……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 5
            - 1
      - text: 但是……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 20
      - text: "\n米法她完成了自己身为英杰的使命。\n如果……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 20
      - text: "我当时能尽到父亲的责任，\n多关心关心她就好了……\n……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 22
      - text: "\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: 林克……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 20
      - text: "\n米法她非常爱你。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 1
      - text: "现在她一定也非常高兴\n自己能够帮助到你卓哟。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 6
      - text: 所以，请你也一定不要忘了她。
      - control:
          kind: choice
