      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 9
      - text: 嗯！你竟然能这么说！
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 20
      - text: "\n真的谢谢你了卓哟！"
  talk07:
    attributes: Npc_Zora003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 5
            - 4
      - text: 林克，要是今后遇到了困难，
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 20
      - text: "\n你随时可以来这片领地。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 1
      - text: "不管何时，我们一族都欢迎你卓哟！\n\n谢谢你，林克……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 20
      - text: "\n谢谢你。"
  talk08:
    attributes: Npc_Zora003
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 1
            - 11
      - text: 谢谢你，林克。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          frames: 20
      - text: "\n是你救了我们卓哟。\n能再次陪伴在你身边，\n米法她一定非常高兴……\n今后，我会在这里守望着\n你们携手战斗卓哟！"
